sequenceDiagram
    autoNumber
    actor EV as Evaluator
    participant UI as  UI
    participant APIG as API Gateway
    participant BFF as Idea  BFF
    participant IS as Idea Service
    participant CS as Campaign Service
    participant DBI as Idea DB
    participant DBC as Campaign DB

    EV->>UI: Click Evaluation tab
    UI->>APIG: GET <br/>/ideas/{ideaId}/stage-config
    APIG->>BFF: Forward request

    BFF->>IS: Get idea <br/>evaluation context
    IS->>DBI: Read IDEA by idea_id
    DBI-->>IS: campaign_id, <br/>current_stage_id

    BFF->>CS: Get stage <br/>questionnaire configuration
    CS->>DBC: Read CAMPAIGN_STAGE <br/>by campaign_id and campaign_stage_id
    DBC-->>CS: stage_name, <br/>stage_weightage_pct

    CS->>DBC: Read CAMPAIGN_STAGE_QUESTION <br/>by campaign_id and campaign_stage_id
    DBC-->>CS: question_text, <br/>scale_min, scale_max, question_weightage_pct

    BFF->>IS: Check draft or <br/>prior evaluation
    IS->>DBI: Read IDEA_EVALUATION <br/>and IDEA_EVALUATION_DETAIL
    DBI-->>IS: Existing draft <br/>scores or no prior record

    BFF-->>APIG: Stage questionnaire <br/>and prior draft
    APIG-->>UI: Load questions and weights

